{"tid":146000,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"全港首部腳玩VR遊戲機　虛擬實景銅鑼灣衝紅燈","createTime":"2017-03-06T16:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T03:54:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"826b00ca87777f2d7fea1c7fedc5a50ce2f8dc9b","tid":146000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T16:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20170305/org/1488639270_6ff5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20170305%2Forg%2F1488639270_6ff5.jpg&h=a00fd294&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/03/04/3291255/20170305_Vsub274AD_clean_w.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvideo.appledaily.com.hk%2Fmcp%2Fencode%2F2017%2F03%2F04%2F3291255%2F20170305_Vsub274AD_clean_w.mp4&d=IX2zbuQlYI18gOdM245y90kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=166591ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://video.appledaily.com.hk/mcp/encode/2017/03/04/3291255/20170305_Vsub274AD_clean_w.mp4</a><br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170305/large/05sub274new1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170305%2Flarge%2F05sub274new1.jpg&h=139e6fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 記者實試用腳玩VR的Virtuix Omni。 <br />\n <br />\nVR眼罩大家也可能曾經玩過，而用腳一起玩的VR裝置相信大家見過亦未必體驗過。這一部Virtuix Omni早於2015年於美國消費電子展現身，等到今年才有一部實體機抵港。記者當然要親身嘗試Omni的威力。 <br />\n <br />\n作為全港首部可以用腳玩VR的裝置，Omni包含體感鞋、保護腰帶以及底座，體感鞋上需要安裝感應器，底部有膠質物料，方便在底座走動，腰部大腿位置都要扣上安全帶。玩家需要額外配備HTC Vive VR眼罩，連同手槍型遙控器一齊使用。Omni猶如汽車遊戲的實體軚盤，不同廠商也可以研發支援Omni的遊戲，而記者試玩的全民槍戰原本為網上遊戲，現在也推出了支援Omni的版本。記者實試後覺得裝置很難控制，雖然安全帶在腰間，但不停轉動會失去方向感，轉動太多亦會容易頭暈。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170305/large/05sub274new2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170305%2Flarge%2F05sub274new2.jpg&h=9d116825&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 美國Worldviz VR系統，可以創造一些虛擬醫療場景，用作培訓模擬手術練習等用途。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170305/large/05sub274new3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170305%2Flarge%2F05sub274new3.jpg&h=51bb68bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Xensory Lab超感研動主席Cheuky Au。 <br />\n <br />\n引入Omni的Xensory Lab超感研動主席Cheuky Au表示：「希望裝置將來也可以引用到打機以外的層面，自己亦與博物館進行磋商，可以虛擬一些博物館，用家可以帶上VR眼罩在Omni上參觀，不用親身到場。」Cheuky亦相信市場對於虛擬場景的需求，引入了美國Worldviz VR系統，配合投影機、感應器、遙控等裝置，可以造出一些虛擬醫療場景，用作培訓模擬手術練習等用途。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170305/large/05sub274new4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170305%2Flarge%2F05sub274new4.jpg&h=5b7e61a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Virtuix Omni需要在體感鞋上安裝感應器。 <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170305/large/05sub274new5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170305%2Flarge%2F05sub274new5.jpg&h=97d4613c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 模擬銅鑼灣街景的虛擬駕駛系統。 <br />\n <br />\n記者亦試玩了另一個虛擬駕駛系統，模擬銅鑼灣街景，而系統亦會記錄衝燈次數以及車速，十分合適學車新手。Cheuky強調：「學車時遇到的突發意外，在現實環境中亦未必經常發生，而虛擬系統則可以模擬一些意外事件，如途人突然衝出路中心，觀察司機的反應如何。」相信大眾日後接觸VR的層面，不再局限於打電子遊戲，日常生活中的應用亦會越來越多。不過，Omni暫時未推出市面，大家想體驗可能要再等等了。<br />\n <br />\n記者：翁怡富<br />\n攝影：徐振國<br />\n <br />\n2017果籽繼續認真知味。識買惜用。行以求知。好事多為。重修舊好。"},{"pid":"9a33e5ffe792cc465ad83869add31fdf2ca50e8d","tid":146000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T17:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510dc8596e12e49cbb071b82d808289d0f81db69","tid":146000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T23:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d4371da2a40dce1c9d40803249b22f7111bdb3","tid":146000,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}